WEBVTT

00:01.800 --> 00:03.080
The second son Xu

00:03.080 --> 00:06.120
With fine qualities and heroic bearing, capable of bearing the divine mandate

00:06.560 --> 00:08.000
Should ascend to the imperial throne

00:08.720 --> 00:11.480
All ministers at home and abroad should assist with one heart

00:12.240 --> 00:15.480
All matters, internal and external, should follow ancestral institutions

00:16.320 --> 00:18.240
Do not fail my trust
